author: scottbw
msg: A substantial rewrite of the proxy service to support full headers being sent and returned, including cookies, and for any content types to be returned in the response body (see WOOKIE-251). Also added more tests, using a NanoHTTPD test server to check that custom headers and cookies are preserved across proxied requests.
